									                		<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.3em; text-align: justify;"><strong>We appreciate your help and support very much</strong>, either by bank transfer or via <strong>PayPal</strong>, which saves a lot of banking fees when you reside outside the EU. Please send us an <span style="color: #4d4d4d; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, FreeSans, sans-serif; line-height: 20px;"><a style="color: #1b57b1; text-decoration: none; font-weight: normal;" title="email" href="https://mail.google.com/a/ecocasa-lapalma.com/mail/?view=cm&amp;fs=1&amp;tf=1&amp;to=presidente@fundacion-drukpa.org" target="_blank">email</a>,</span> indicating what you want your donation to be used for. We strictly separate and distribute funds in these categories:</p>
<ol>
<li>Disaster relief,</li>
<li>helping poor and sick people in need,</li>
<li>animal help, rescue, feeding, sterilizations or veterinary costs,</li>
<li>adoption and support for a specific animal (dog or donkey) on a regular basis,</li>
<li>environmental activities to protect nature.</li>
</ol>
<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.3em;">Bank account holder: Drukpa, Fundación Canaria,<br /> Bank: BBVA, Los Llanos de Aridane, Spain,<br /> Account Number: <span style="color: #4d4d4d; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, FreeSans, sans-serif; line-height: 20px;">0182 3630 80 020 1535989, </span><span style="color: #4d4d4d; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, FreeSans, sans-serif; line-height: 20px;"><br />IBAN: ES7401823630800201535989, BIC: BBVAESMM.</span></p>
